## ⚙️ Bibliotecas e Stack

```html
<!-- GSAP (ScrollSmoother é gratuito via CDN do GSAP) -->
<script src="https://cdn.gsap.com/public/gsap-trial/3.12.5/gsap.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.gsap.com/public/gsap-trial/3.12.5/ScrollTrigger.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.gsap.com/public/gsap-trial/3.12.5/ScrollSmoother.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.gsap.com/public/gsap-trial/3.12.5/ScrollToPlugin.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.gsap.com/public/gsap-trial/3.12.5/SplitText.min.js"></script>
```

```js
gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger, ScrollSmoother, ScrollToPlugin, SplitText);

// Init do ScrollSmoother — estrutura obrigatória no HTML
ScrollSmoother.create({
  wrapper: "#smooth-wrapper",
  content: "#smooth-content",
  smooth: 1.5,
  effects: true,
});
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Se ScrollSmoother gerar erros (licença), trocar por **Lenis** (MIT gratuito) com ScrollTrigger.

**HTML obrigatório:**
```html
<div id="smooth-wrapper">
  <div id="smooth-content">
    <!-- TODO o site vai aqui -->
  </div>
</div>
```

